  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">Either they didnt listen to it all, its official Tory line or they think people not listening. Norfolk deserves better, much better. We deserve MPs &amp; councillors who work together rather than bad mouth their own side in public. I wonder what they call each other in private!<a href="https://t.co/CGnbiJiZD4" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/emmalhampton/status/974287292486553601" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/emmalhampton/status/974287292486553601"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/emmalhampton/s</span><span class="invisible">tatus/974287292486553601</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>

          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">Remarkable that <span class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="1010947814"><s>@</s><b>NorfolkTories</b></span> think this is an interview worth them publicising. During it, Cllr Jordan - Tory leader of Norfolk County Council - says the county's MPs (7/9 of whom are Tory) "might as well not be there" and that he's "just fed up with listening to them". </div>

<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">When I shop I go round the supermarket Ive been going to for the last 40 years. What I dont do is slam its door shut, then wander round the world for 10 years looking for other little shops that might one day sell me the same stuff but  at higher prices cos they know im a mug.<a href="https://t.co/X84RxZeVO4" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/johnredwood/status/969152882854518784" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/johnredwood/status/969152882854518784"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/johnredwood/st</span><span class="invisible">atus/969152882854518784</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Tony Robinson added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/johnredwood/status/969152882854518784" data-conversation-id="969152882854518784" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="969152882854518784" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="johnredwood" data-user-id="93880122" href="/johnredwood/status/969152882854518784" data-conversation-id="969152882854518784" tabindex="0">
      <div class="tweet-content">
        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
            
  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">
    <b class="QuoteTweet-fullname u-linkComplex-target">John Redwood</b><span class="UserBadges"></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>johnredwood</b></span>
  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">When I shop I do not put cash on the counter &amp; then ask what the shop might have in return. I ask to see the goods, ask the price &amp; then decide whether to buy. The EU wants us to shop the wrong way round. They expect us to put up a lot of money without telling us what it buys.</div>

</div>

          <p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="1">Jeremy Corbyn Retweeted The Labour Party</p>


<div class="js-tweet-text-container">
  <p class="TweetTextSize TweetTextSize--normal js-tweet-text tweet-text" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="4">.<a href="/theresa_may" class="twitter-atreply pretty-link js-nav" dir="ltr" data-mentioned-user-id="747807250819981312"><s>@</s><b>Theresa_May</b></a>, we dont need a review into university tuition fees, we need them to be scrapped.<a href="https://t.co/Kh2drSO92F" rel="nofollow noopener" dir="ltr" data-expanded-url="https://twitter.com/UKLabour/status/967699230323363840" class="twitter-timeline-link u-hidden" target="_blank" title="https://twitter.com/UKLabour/status/967699230323363840"><span class="tco-ellipsis"></span><span class="invisible">https://</span><span class="js-display-url">twitter.com/UKLabour/statu</span><span class="invisible">s/967699230323363840</span><span class="tco-ellipsis"><span class="invisible"></span></span></a></p>
</div>


<p class="u-hiddenVisually" aria-hidden="true" data-aria-label-part="3">Jeremy Corbyn added,</p>
  
      <div class="QuoteTweet&#10;    &#10;    &#10;    u-block js-tweet-details-fixer">
  <div class="QuoteTweet-container">
    <a class="QuoteTweet-link js-nav" href="/UKLabour/status/967699230323363840" data-conversation-id="967699230323363840" aria-hidden="true">
    </a>
    <div class="QuoteTweet-innerContainer u-cf js-permalink js-media-container" data-item-id="967699230323363840" data-item-type="tweet" data-screen-name="UKLabour" data-user-id="14291684" href="/UKLabour/status/967699230323363840" data-conversation-id="967699230323363840" tabindex="0">
      <div class="tweet-content">
            <div class="QuoteMedia">

        <div class="QuoteTweet-authorAndText u-alignTop">
            
  <div class="QuoteTweet-originalAuthor u-cf u-textTruncate stream-item-header account-group js-user-profile-link">
    <b class="QuoteTweet-fullname u-linkComplex-target">The Labour Party</b><span class="UserBadges"><span class="Icon Icon--verified"><span class="u-hiddenVisually">Verified account</span></span></span><span class="UserNameBreak"></span><span class="username u-dir u-textTruncate" dir="ltr">@<b>UKLabour</b></span>
  </div>

          
          
          <div class="QuoteTweet-text tweet-text u-dir" lang="en" data-aria-label-part="2" dir="ltr">The Tories have tripled uni fees and slashed further education funding. Now all theyre offering is a review of their broken system.
We dont need a review, we need real change now.</div>
        </div>
      </div>

    When you see a Tweet you love, tap the heart  it lets  the person who wrote it know that you appreciate them.
  </p>
